summary: This document is a Placement Agent Warrant issued by Aptorum Group Limited, dated October 14, 2025, which allows the holder to purchase a specific number of Ordinary Shares at an exercise price of $2.50 per share. The warrant can be exercised starting from the initial exercise date until the earlier of 24 months after the effective date of a resale registration statement or October 10, 2030. The warrant includes provisions for cashless exercise if there is no effective registration statement for the resale of the shares.
